    • loadPlotData

      public PlotBlockData loadPlotData(TownBlock townBlock)
      Load PlotBlockData for regen at unclaim First attempts to load a .zip file containing the data file. Fallback attempts to load old .data files instead. Once it finds a zip or data file it will send it to be unpacked by loadDataStream(PlotBlockData, InputStream) which will return the populated PlotBlockData object.
      Specified by:
      loadPlotData in class TownyDataSource
      Parameters:
      townBlock - - townBlock being reverted
      Returns:
      PlotBlockData or null
